=== Windswept Planet ===
:1. '''''Windswept Planet''''', gives {{reward|gas|mat1}}
:* {{icon|astral rift difficulty easy}} 2 ''"Rise above the storm."'', proceed to '''''Beyond the Stratosphere'''''.
:* {{icon|astral rift difficulty easy}} 2 ''"Shelter in the cave below."'', proceed to '''''Fungal Cavern'''''.
:Chose ''"Rise above the storm."'':
::2. '''''Beyond the Stratosphere''''', ''"Take a sample of the wind."'', gives {{reward|ast|ast1|empty|empty}}
::3. '''''Living Wind''''', ''"Follow the living wind."'' gives {{reward|ast|ast1|empty|empty}}
::4. '''''Fungal Threat''''', gives {{reward|ast|ast1|empty|empty}}, choice:
::* {{icon|astral rift difficulty hard}} 6 ''"Find a way to remove the fungus."'', pay {{icon|alloys}} 25 alloys, proceed to '''''Cutting Winds'''''
::* {{icon|astral rift difficulty normal}} 3 ''"Investigate the fungus."'', proceed to '''''Fungal Transmission'''''.
::5. '''''Fungal Transmission''''', ''"Decipher the fungal transmission."'', gives {{reward|ast|ast1|empty|empty}}, proceed to '''''The Case for the Fungus'''''.
:Chose ''"Shelter in the cave below."'':
::2. '''''Fungal Cavern''''', ''"Attempt to communicate."'', gives {{reward|ast|ast1|empty|empty}}
::3. '''''Among the Fungus''''', ''"Maintain fungal correspondence."'', gives {{reward|ast|ast1|empty|empty}}
::4. '''''Carnivorous Winds''''', gives {{reward|ast|ast1|empty|empty}}, choice:
::* {{icon|astral rift difficulty hard}} 6 ''"Protect the ecosystem against the wind."'', pay {{icon|minerals}} 50 minerals, proceed to '''''Fungal Bloom'''''
::* {{icon|astral rift difficulty normal}} 3 ''"Study the wind."'', proceed to '''''Current Events'''''.
::5. '''''Current Events''''', ''"Continue the investigation."'', gives {{reward|ast|ast1|empty|empty}}, proceed to '''''The Case for the Wind'''''.
:6. '''''The Case for the Fungus / Wind''''', gives {{reward|ast|ast1|empty|empty}}
:* {{icon|astral rift difficulty normal}} 3 ''"Fortify the wind."'', pay {{icon|alloys}} 25 alloys, proceed to '''''Cutting Winds'''''
:* {{icon|astral rift difficulty normal}} 3 ''"Nourish the fungus."'', pay {{icon|minerals}} 50 minerals, proceed to '''''Fungal Bloom'''''
:* {{icon|astral rift difficulty hard}} 6 ''"Negotiate a compromise."'', proceed to '''''A Difficult Compromise''''' (available if {{icon|no}}{{icon|fanatic purifiers}}{{icon|devouring swarm}}{{icon|determined exterminator}} Genocidal)
:* {{icon|astral rift difficulty hard}} 6 ''"Eradicate both species."'', proceed to '''''Biological Eradication''''' (available if {{icon|fanatic purifiers}}{{icon|devouring swarm}}{{icon|determined exterminator}} Genocidal)
