: Regardless of outcome, ends the rift.

If the rift concluded with the '''''A Difficult Compromise''''' outcome, the '''''A Special Request''''' event will trigger in a few days, giving you the option to convert the scientist into an envoy and gain the ''Reconverted Leader'' modifier, granting {{icon|available envoys}} {{green|+1}} available envoys.
